            <title>
                <![CDATA[加密货币恐怖融资争议：Chainalysis 警惕夸大与误解]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以巴冲突发生后，关于以加密货币资助恐怖份子的争论不断。包括币安和 Tether 都表示，己配合冻结多个帐户和地址，以切断哈玛斯加密金援。反加密出名的参议员 Elizabeth Warren 趁势推动《数位资产反洗钱法案》，要求拜登政府月底前有所回应！但链上分析公司 Chainalysis 有些看不下去了！对于某些夸大指标和有缺陷的分析，<a href="https://www.chainalysis.com/blog/cryptocurrency-terrorism-financing-accuracy-check/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chainalysis 特别撰文</a>纠正一些误解。</p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/israel-orders-freeze-on-crypto-accounts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以色列下令冻结加密地址！扣押数百万美元资产，目标切断哈玛斯加密金援</a>)</p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/hamas-is-no-longer-received-cryto-due-to-the-transparency" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哈马斯加密钱包成焦点：推动数位资产反洗钱法案？哈马斯都知道加密货币具可追溯性</a>)</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/chainalysis-cryptocurrency-terrorism-financing-accuracy-check#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65311dc87a787"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
